<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ALASKA Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family:'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
        }
        /* Header Styles */
        .header {
            background-color: #00f5b7;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
          .header > h1{
            color: white;
          }
        /* Button Styles */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e3ecf5;
            color: #060505;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: 2px dashed rgb(147, 147, 222);
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
       
        /* Footer Styles */
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .footer > p{
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to ALASKA!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content" style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>Thank you for signing up <%= user.name %>. To activate your account, please use the below code:</p>
            <h2 class="btn"><%= activationCode %></h2>
            <p>Please enter the code to activate your account. This code will deactivate after 5 minutes</p>
           
            <p>If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Our Website Team</p>
            <p>If you have any quary please contact us <a href="karmakarnirjus4839@gmail.com">karmakarnirjus4839@gmail.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
